```python
def make_song(string):
    syllable = {'도':note_do, '레':note_re, '미':note_mi, '파':note_pa, '솔':note_sol, '라':note_la, '시':note_si, ' ':note_0}
    song = np.array([])
    for note in string:
        song = np.append(song, syllable[note])
    return ipd.Audio(song, rate=sr)
```

### melspectrogram

<div class="in_prompt">
In&nbsp;[33]:
</div>

<div class="input_area" markdown="1">

```python
D = abs(librosa.stft(sound_contents))
mel_spec = librosa.feature.melspectrogram(S=D, n_mels=30) # n_mels: 적절한 구분으로 구간을 나눔
mel_db = librosa.amplitude_to_db(mel_spec, ref=0.000001)

librosa.display.specshow(mel_db, sr=file_sampling_rate, x_axis='time', y_axis='mel')
plt.title('mel freq power spectrogram')
plt.colorbar(format='%+2.0f dB')
plt.show()
```

</div>

<div class="output_prompt">
Out&nbsp;[33]:
